org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM members LEFT OUTER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id LEFT OUTER JOIN member_roles ON member_roles.member_id = members.id LEFT OUTER JOIN roles ON roles.id = member_roles.role_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND (projects.active = True OR project_id IS NULL) LIMIT 1
